data.description: This lovely two story 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom 2712 SF home sits on higher, green ground! Upon entering, notice the beautiful, low maintenance floors in living areas, LED lights and blinds for your comfort. The kitchen has plenty of storage, Energy Star appliances, easy to clean surfaces and sitting island. The open floorplan is great for entertaining and has wonderful natural light. Bedrooms are spacious, allow for extra furniture and have walk-in closets. A covered porch in the front for you to enjoy those starry nights. The neighbors are on lower terrain, the view is all yours to enjoy!
